# SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE

## Controller Layer
- Arduino UNO:
  Handles movement and Bluetooth control

- Arduino Nano:
  Handles interaction systems and OLED rendering

---

## Sensor Layer
- Ultrasonic sensor:
  User/object detection

- Touch sensor:
  Interaction trigger

---

## Output Layer
- OLED:
  Facial expressions

- Servo:
  Lid mechanism

- Motors:
  Robot mobility
